StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetProspectPhysicalProblems]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@ProspectID uniqueiden..er
AS BEGIN SET NOCOUNT ON SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT ProspectId INTO #ProspectId FROM Prospec.ng.USMC.Prospect WHERE ProspectId = @ProspectID
SELECT ppp.ProspectPhysicalProblemsId, ppp.ProspectId, ppp.Implants, ppp.Contacts, ppp.Opera.ons, ppp.Medicines, ppp.BrokenBones, ppp.Asthma, ppp.Tatoos, ppp.Vision, ppp.Other FROM Prospec.ng.USMC.ProspectPhysicalProblems ppp INNER JOIN #ProspectId p ON ppp.ProspectId = p.ProspectId
DROP TABLE #ProspectId END
